item.title: 【Requests】[REQ AUD] - (REQ) SZA & Justin Bieber - Snooze
item.description: I don't know why they decided to make it an acoustic version, but I'd love if somebody could edit it with the original instrumental. I mean, I asked for this when Perfect Duet came out and no one ever attempted to do it lol, but I did see a solo remix version of Bad Blood, so I believe it is possible.
item.author: Angel1989
